article.description: — Trey Townsend scored 25 points and Oakland held off Rice 76-73 on Tuesday night in the Gulf Coast Showcase.
article.headline: Oakland hangs on for 76-73 win over Rice
article.linkText: Oakland hangs on for 76-73 win over Rice
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Trey Townsend scored 25 points and Oakland held off Rice 76-73 on Tuesday night in the Gulf Coast Showcase. Jamal Cain had 19 points for Oakland (4-2). Jalen Moore added 13 points. Carl Pierre had 22 points for the Owls (4-2). Chris Mullins added 17 points and Travis Evee had 11. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
